48
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:16,590
Bai Xia,

49
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,030
I promise you.

50
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,560
On behalf of my daughter,

51
00:02:19,910 --> 00:02:21,400
