[Shen Jiahe]

85
00:03:41,470 --> 00:03:43,280
Luckily, Shen Jiahe arrived in time.

86
00:03:43,590 --> 00:03:44,400
Or who knows

87
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,310
what she'd have done?

88
00:03:46,710 --> 00:03:47,520
Do you really know

89
