102
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:08,910
All right.

103
00:04:09,590 --> 00:04:10,240
Go ahead.

104
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,430
Hurry up.

105
00:04:23,540 --> 00:04:25,820
[Shen]

106
00:04:25,820 --> 00:04:27,500
[Shen Jiahe]

107
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,720
Aunt Pei, open the door!

108
00:04:50,270 --> 00:04:50,800
Stop.

109
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,430
Mr. Xu,

110
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,000
