124
00:05:29,190 --> 00:05:29,920
Look at you!

125
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:31,360
Look at what you've done!

126
00:05:31,510 --> 00:05:32,510
Do you think causing trouble

127
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:34,430
only hurts Bai Xia's reputation?

128
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,870
It's not Bai Xia's.

129
00:05:35,950 --> 00:05:38,240
It's Yuanfei Group's and mine!

130
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:39,920
Who's to blame for that?

131
00:05:40,830 --> 00:05:41,480
If you hadn't cheated,

132
00:05:41,510 --> 00:05:42,510
would any of this have happened?

133
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:43,430
Oh,

134
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,650
your mother and I

135
00:05:45,650 --> 00:05:46,680
