136
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,800
Why must you insist

137
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:49,600
on binding me to her forever?

138
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:50,950
Can't your father find someone new

139
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,120
after a divorce?

140
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:54,680
You really think Bai Xia

141
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,800
truly loves you?

142
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,270
What does she see in you?

143
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,560
Your age?

144
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,310
Or your money?

145
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:01,360
Are you really that clueless?

146
00:06:01,390 --> 00:06:02,430
What did you say?

147
00:06:13,390 --> 00:06:14,190
You hit me?

148
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,430
You'll regret this!

149
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,240
Nuo!

150
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:27,360
Nuo...

151
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:39,120
Your parents' divorce

152
00:06:39,430 --> 00:06:41,160
really wasn't because of Bai Xia.

153
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,630
When Bai Xia met your dad,

154
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,000
your parents were already

155
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:46,870
in the process of divorcing.

156
00:06:47,950 --> 00:06:48,720
Are you sure?

157
00:06:53,510 --> 00:06:54,830
Then did Bai Xia meet my dad

158
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,430
through Shen Jiahe?

159
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:00,040
We didn't find out yet,

160
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:02,120
but it's probably the case.

161
00:07:02,630 --> 00:07:03,920
Otherwise, it's too much of a coincidence.

162
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,560
Could it be

163
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:08,310
that Bai Xia couldn't be with Shen Jiahe all these years,

164
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,510
so she held a grudge

165
00:07:10,630 --> 00:07:11,920
and decided to become his stepmom?

166
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,800
You've watched too many dramas.

167
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,830
Bai Xia isn't the romantic type.

168
00:07:20,830 --> 00:07:22,510
No matter what Bai Xia's intentions are,

169
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:25,360
either Shen Jiahe is using her

170
00:07:25,390 --> 00:07:26,310
to please my dad,

171
00:07:26,630 --> 00:07:28,360
