172
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:30,310
to solidify his position in Yuanfei Group.

173
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,000
Then...

174
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,240
why is Shen Jiahe

175
00:07:35,310 --> 00:07:36,870
still helping Aunt Rong fight for assets

176
00:07:36,870 --> 00:07:37,750
and the house?

177
00:07:38,830 --> 00:07:40,360
Even though Grandma passed away,

178
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,120
my uncle is still Yuanfei Group's major shareholder.

179
00:07:42,510 --> 00:07:43,560
He probably wants

180
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,630
to leave himself an escape route.

181
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:48,310
But from what I've seen,

182
00:07:49,870 --> 00:07:51,800
he's always been kind to Aunt Rong.

183
00:07:59,310 --> 00:08:00,870
