188
00:08:19,390 --> 00:08:21,070
Maybe he had his reasons.

189
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,600
If you talked it out...

190
00:08:22,630 --> 00:08:23,480
Absolutely impossible.

191
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,870
Just consider it

192
00:08:28,870 --> 00:08:29,720
my poor judgment before.

193
00:08:33,030 --> 00:08:34,390
