197
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:04,670
Dad,

198
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,510
don't worry.

199
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,270
No matter what,

200
00:09:09,510 --> 00:09:10,750
I'll settle the debts

201
00:09:11,550 --> 00:09:13,120
